b'PM: "This new economy will be more adaptive, flexible and able to seize new opportunities than ever before."'
b'PM: \xe2\x80\x9cIn this decade, Australia can build a rich, fair economy \xe2\x80\x93 where working people get their share of the benefits.\xe2\x80\x9d'

b'PM: "While economic transformations are never easy, this time we have an advantage we have rarely had before."'
